title: Lancôme Livestream Event | January 12, 2018 | HSN
description:
Join Lancôme for a live digital event 
Lancôme begins celebrating 10 years at HSN with their Top 10 Best Sellers list 
Robert and Cara will be LIVE offering tips and answering questions as they reveal Lancôme’s Top 10 Best Sellers list 

Watch Friday, January 12 at 1:15pm ET

Shop HSN and Lancôme
